{{ if and .TransientPayload (eq (index .TransientPayload "verify_type") "commit_lifeai") }}Anda baru saja mengajukan permintaan Commit Life Points dari dompet Anda. Berikut adalah kode OTP untuk mengonfirmasi transaksi ini:

{{ .VerificationCode }}

Detail transaksi:
Jumlah Commit (LP): {{ index .TransientPayload "amount" }}

Silakan masukkan kode OTP ini untuk melanjutkan transaksi Commit Life Points Anda.

OTP hanya berlaku selama {{ .ExpiresInMinutes }} menit ke depan. Jangan bagikan kode ini kepada siapa pun.

Terima kasih telah bersama {{ .Tenant }}! Jika memerlukan bantuan, silakan hubungi kami di support@lifenetwork.ai.

Hormat kami,
Tim {{ .Tenant }}
{{ else if and .TransientPayload (eq (index .TransientPayload "verify_type") "commit_unity") }}You have just requested to commit Life Points from your wallet. Here is your One-Time Password (OTP) to verify your commitment transaction:

{{ .VerificationCode }}

Transaction details:
Commitment amount (LP): {{ index .TransientPayload "amount" }}

Please enter this OTP to proceed with your Life Points commitment.

Your OTP will be valid for {{ .ExpiresInMinutes }} minutes. Do not share this OTP with anyone.

Thank you for choosing {{ .Tenant }}! If you need any assistance, feel free to reach out to us at support@lifenetwork.ai.

Best regards,
The {{ .Tenant }} Team
{{ else if and .TransientPayload (eq (index .TransientPayload "verify_type") "withdraw_main_wallet") }}We have received a request to withdraw{{ if and .TransientPayload (index .TransientPayload "amount") }} {{ index .TransientPayload "amount" }}{{ end }} USDT from your LIFE AI account. For security reasons, please use the One-Time Password (OTP) provided below to confirm this transaction.

{{ .VerificationCode }}

Please enter this OTP in the LIFE AI app to proceed with your transaction.

Your OTP will be valid for {{ .ExpiresInMinutes }} minutes. Do not share this OTP with anyone.

Thank you for choosing LIFE AI! If you need any assistance, feel free to reach out to us at support@lifenetwork.ai.

Best regards,
LIFE AI Support Team
{{ else if and .TransientPayload (eq (index .TransientPayload "verify_type") "withdraw_unity") }}We have received a request to withdraw{{ if and .TransientPayload (index .TransientPayload "amount") }} {{ index .TransientPayload "amount" }}{{ end }} USDT from your LIFE Unity account. For security reasons, please use the One-Time Password (OTP) provided below to confirm this transaction.

